claim: Sweden has a lower COVID-19 death rate than Spain, Italy and the U.K., even though it never had a lockdown
label: Misleading

claim: The web page “Bolivia Segura”, official site of the Government of Bolivia on COVID-19, reported a faithful data of the deaths on Saturday, August 8, 2020
label: MISLEADING

claim: A large, country-randomized controlled trial with 2.7 billion people shows that COVID-19 patients treated with hydroxychloroquine have a 79.1% lower death rate
label: FALSE

claim: Multiple Facebook posts shared thousands of times claim the Australian government paid nursing homes AUS$25,000 for “labelling [COVID-19] as the main cause of deaths on death certificates”. label: FALSE

claim: Brazilian Civil Registry data shows that country records fewer deaths in July 2020 than July 2019
label: MISLEADING

claim: If masks were effective and necessary, non-mask wearers should be dead by now
label: FALSE

claim: A video supposedly showing a dead COVID-19 victim raising his hand while being lifted away by health workers proves the global pandemic is a hoax.
label: FALSE

claim: Scientists wear hazmat suits to protect themselves from deadly viruses so masks are not effective against COVID-19
label: MISLEADING

claim: A long Facebook post, allegedly written by Anthony Fauci (the director of NIAID in the United States) shows the author reject the idea that COVID-19 is “just a virus” and that “we’ll all get it eventually”.
label: FALSE

claim: Arturo Murillo affirmed that in the last three days 170 death bodies were collected from the city of El Alto.
label: False

claim: COVID-19 death rate is lower in post-Soviet states than in the US
label: MISLEADING

claim: The pandemic was planned at Event 201. There are different Satanic symbols, which appear along with pandemic, e.g., Egyptian death deity Anubis and red-eyed mustang in Denver.

claim: Multiple Facebook posts shared hundreds of times claim “viruses do not harm or kill [people]” and that any “harm and death” caused by a virus can be attributed to “the overreaction of a weakened and dysfunctional immune system”.
